metadata.name: DinoMonks VX #1
metadata.description:
DinoMonks VX is the NFT collection bringing Mental Health and Wellness into the Metaverse. 

Venture into a universe of understanding, compassion and support with the Dinomonk VX collection. There are 5,500 DinoMonk VX's who will act as your avatar as you journey into the DinoMonk Sanctuary within the Sandbox.

DinoMonks is a community that values wellness and community support above all. Visit the DinoMonks community for any and all of the support structures we have in place.
